    "When on, the hierarchy expand/collapse state is restored per target-app bundle id across host and target-app restarts. The 20 most recently inspected apps are kept; toggling off preserves existing data but stops reading or writing it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, the hierarchy expand/collapse state is restored per target-app bundle id across host and target-app restarts. The 20 most recently inspected apps are kept; toggling off preserves existing data but stops reading or writing it."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，将按目标 App 的 bundle id 在宿主和目标 App 重启后恢复层级展开/折叠状态。会保留最近检查的 20 个 App；关闭后会保留已有数据，但停止读取或写入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
